  <h1>BIHS Summer Discovery Series</h1>
  <p>Join over a dozen international scholars exploring consciousness, ethics, cosmology, and more — in a space where devotion meets discovery.</p>

  <h3>How It Works:</h3>
  <p>The series is hosted via Zoom, but all links, recordings, and updates are managed through Canvas Instructure. This gives participants a single, clean place to stay engaged.</p>

  <h3>Already on Canvas?</h3>
  <p>If you're already taking another BIHS course, simply <strong>check your inbox</strong> for an invite to this series. If you're logged in, <a href="https://canvas.instructure.com">click here</a> to accept directly.</p>

  <h3>New to Canvas?</h3>
  <p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Please do not sign up with Google, Gmail, or Facebook — this often causes login issues.</p>
  <p>To register manually:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Go to <a href="https://canvas.instructure.com/register" target="_blank">https://canvas.instructure.com/register</a></li>
    <li>Select "I’m a Student"</li>
    <li>Create your account with username and password</li>
    <li>Use the join code: <strong>CR4PDK</strong></li>
  </ol>
